{"tid":967721,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜 想搵人秒回 圍爐 呻下","createTime":"2019-01-03T17:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T18:13:25.000Z","uid":25145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9426bff5e657170a3cb2ef8abee1fd825eeaa2","tid":967721,"uid":25145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"講下背景先 <br />\n小弟今年22<br />\n屋企中産家庭 <br />\n以前做過player <br />\n<br />\n係打機識左個28嘅姐姐 之後一齊左 好鍾意佢 本身諗住咁就一世 有諗過娶佢<br />\n<br />\n為左個女仔戒酒戒浦無食煙 不停搵份好工 儲錢結婚（屋企人有多間屋所以我唔使儲錢買）進修 朝朝做gym 想健康D想佢有個大隻男朋友會開心D<br />\n<br />\n點知俾佢屋企人一句唔成熟 𡃁仔唔可信 女仔屋企人每日煩佢 搞到我同佢成日鬧交 之後就變左ex <br />\n<br />\n到依家唔敢再拍拖 連識人嘅動力都無 但係去到大時大節見到個個都有人陪 自己就一個人 真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好掛住你呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知佢無上連登 <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"9a8654917acc222733ce29c054c999c68523f042","tid":967721,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09c3116e275cd2027f95626bbd5a63c74cda1131","tid":967721,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34c33e395423b6e9e5f848f3f9c61fbd93ff94ac","tid":967721,"uid":25145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a8654917acc222733ce29c054c999c68523f042","tid":967721,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"小妺妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5ff69971e0e46a31706fd9f69f0de525eb9ccd","tid":967721,"uid":25145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c3116e275cd2027f95626bbd5a63c74cda1131","tid":967721,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":